      <item>
        <title>Streaming message</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[@primadude Primadude]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
          <p><a href="https://forum.moparisthebest.com/u/primadude">@primadude</a> wrote:</p>
          <blockquote>
              <p>[quote=“Newty, post:4, topic:276001”]Declare a timer:</p>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">int timeToMessage = 60;</code></pre>
<p>Make it countdown: Add the following in the process method:</p>
<p><code>
if (timeToMessage &gt; 0) {
timeToMessage--;
}
if (timeToMessage == 0) {
sendMessage("Whatever you want");
timeToMessage = 60;
}
</code>[/quote]</p>
<p>This is better:</p>
<p>[code]long timeToMessage;</p>
<p>if (System.currentTimeMillis() - timeToMessage &gt;= 60000) {<br>
sendMessage(“Whatever you want.”);<br>
timeToMessage = System.currentTimeMillis();<br>
}[/code]</p>
<p>60000 Milliseconds = 60 seconds.</p>
          </blockquote>
          <p><a href="https://forum.moparisthebest.com/t/streaming-message/276001/5">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
